    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently faces significant mechanical challenges, including an engine that runs roughly and a transmission that struggles to shift properly. The exterior shows its age with multiple dents, paint fading, and some rust spots, while the interior has significant tearing in the upholstery and several broken trim pieces. This would be an ideal project car for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts vehicle, as it will require substantial work to be roadworthy again.",
